Enclosing class:
LcarsApp.DesktopCanvas
private class LcarsApp.DesktopCanvas.Tile extends javafx.scene.layout.StackPane
Draggable LCARS tile for a Desktop file. Dropping over the trash target attempts to move the file back to its origin directory (copy+delete fallback).
